    "groupAbout": "About",
    "aboutTagline": "A quiet, focused todo companion that keeps your attention where it belongs — on what matters.",
    "aboutBody": "TodoApp brings quick tasks and long-term goals into one calm, focused space. Deadline reminders keep you on track, the built-in focus timer helps you enter a flow state, and one-click exports to JSON, CSV, or a polished PDF report let you share or archive your progress anytime. Everything is stored locally on your device, isolated per account — private, yours, always.",
    "aboutHighlights": "Why TodoApp",
    "aboutHighlightsBody": "A distraction-free interface keeps you focused on tasks, not tooling. Light and dark themes plus full bilingual support (Chinese / English) adapt to any context. A global hotkey summons the app instantly without breaking your focus. Focus timer, deadline alerts, data backup, and multi-format export — one app, complete workflow.",
    "aboutCompare": "How we compare",
    "aboutCompareBody": "Unlike mainstream todo apps that require accounts, cloud sync, and monthly subscriptions, TodoApp is local-first: no sign-up, no recurring fees, no data leaving your device. The quick/long-term task split plus deadline reminders reduce missed items that flat lists often lose. A built-in focus timer means you no longer juggle a separate Pomodoro app. If you want a reliable, calm task manager that stays out of your way, TodoApp was built for exactly that.",
